# Documentation: Bd decay to K* tau tau.
# One tau lepton decays in the 3 charged pions (as in event type 11110000) 
# or in the 3 charged pions plus a pi0 modes (as in event type 11716400).
# All final-state charged products in the acceptance.
# 
# EndDocumentation
