# Tauola steering options
Define TauolaCurrentOption 1
Define TauolaBR1 1.0
#
Alias         Mytau1+      tau+
Alias         Mytau2-      tau-
ChargeConj    Mytau1+      Mytau2-
Alias         Mytau2+      tau+
Alias         Mytau1-      tau-
ChargeConj    Mytau2+      Mytau1-
Alias         MyK*0        K*0
Alias         Myanti-K*0   anti-K*0
ChargeConj    MyK*0        Myanti-K*0
#
Decay B0sig
  0.500       MyK*0      Mytau1-      Mytau1+        BTOSLLBALL;
  0.500       MyK*0      Mytau2+      Mytau2-        BTOSLLBALL;
Enddecay
Decay anti-B0sig
  0.500       Myanti-K*0      Mytau1-      Mytau1+        BTOSLLBALL;
  0.500       Myanti-K*0      Mytau2+      Mytau2-        BTOSLLBALL;
Enddecay
#
Decay MyK*0
  1.000       K+         pi-          VSS;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-K*0
#
Decay Mytau1-
  9.31        TAUOLA 5;
  4.62        TAUOLA 8;
Enddecay
#
Decay Mytau1+
  1.00        mu+        nu_mu        anti-nu_tau   TAULNUNU;
Enddecay
#       
Decay Mytau2+
  9.02        TAUOLA 5;
  4.49        TAUOLA 8;
Enddecay
#
Decay Mytau2-
  1.00        mu-        anti-nu_mu   nu_tau        TAULNUNU;
Enddecay      
#
End
